      "message": "1st problem: The whitespace changes are caused by replacing a space with a non-breakable space, and \u0027straight\u0027 ASCII double quotes are getting converted to \u0027curly\u0027 left/right quotes. This is probably some auto-formatting setting in your editor -- it should be easy to disable.\n\n2nd problem: The character encoding seems to be Latin-1. Set your editor to UTF-8 instead.\n\nIt seems only this file has these issues. You can revert to the original state with git:\n\n    git checkout origin/master -- apps/iap/iap-lingo4.c\n\nThen you can do the intended change without the editor \"helpfully\" reformatting the file :)",
